window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Many Christians love to experience the classic sermons of the great 19th-century English preacher Charles H. Spurgeon. But there were many other Christian writers of the same era who also penned inspired devotionals, including C. H. Spurgeon, US President James Buchanan, and the writer of the classic hymn \"Amazing Grace\", John Newton. </p><p>In volume two of this collection of timeless treasures are 10 classic devotionals from 29 inspired writers. These devotions are performed for a modern audience by the unique and emotive voice of British narrator Christopher Glyn. <i>Faith of Our Fathers</i> will enrich and strengthen your spiritual life and walk with the Lord as you enjoy these inspirational devotions. </p>"; 
